
## 📁 Project Structure

```
Learning_Playwright/
├── chap1/               # Chapter 1 – JavaScript Fundamentals
│   ├── ex1.js           # Basics: console output, process info
│   ├── ex2 JS.js        # Loops, functions, and variable scope
│   ├── hotcode.js       # Hot code paths and performance basics
│   └── verify version.js
├── chap2/               # Chapter 2 – (Coming soon)
├── .gitignore
└── README.md
```

## 🚀 Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/) (v16 or later)
- [npm](https://www.npmjs.com/)

### Installation

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/prriyaldesai-prog/Learning_Playwright.git
cd Learning_Playwright

# Install Playwright
npm init -y
npm install playwright
```

### Running Examples

```bash
# Run a chapter 1 exercise
node chap1/ex1.js
```

